Program: Free Thinking
Title: Tourism past and present
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m00021kq
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 16 Jan 2019
The must-see sights on the Grand Tour, in Cold War Moscow and tourist hot spots now. Rana Mitter is joined by Roey Sweet, Sarah Goldsmith, Nick Barnett, Cindy Yu and Simon Calder. Producer: Torquil MacLeod.